title: Dalm Eun Sarang (Forbidden Love OST)
lyrics: jichin maeumeui kkeuteseo dasi kkumeul kkurago dasi ooseulsoo isseulkkeorago geudae seulpeun noonbicheuro jakeun daedapeul haessjiman naneun deureulsooga eobseoyo nal wihae saragal geu manheun sigane I gaseumeseo neolbonaeulsoon eobseo          naega geudae dwil suga eobsgie neomoo manheun apeumeul oorin dalmeungeoya wiroome jichin ooril wihae ijen sojoonghan jasineul akkyeoyahae jigeumboda deohan apeumi nal chajawado yeongwonhi saranghal soo bakke eobseo oonmyeong gatteun ooyeoni ooril kidarijianha sarange hanil jirado nal wihae saragal geu manheun sigane I gaseumeseo neolbonaeulsoon eobseo          ttu ttu ttu ttu ttu ttu ttu ttu ttu ttu
